    "Do not broaden unrelated commands.",
    "Do not claim full pairtools parity beyond committed oracle fixtures.",
    "Do not run benchmarks or claim speedup.",
    "Pairtools may be used only as a test oracle.",
    "Do not implement arbitrary Python execution or startup-code behavior in Rust runtime."
  ],
